# CLAUDE.md — Claude Code adapter for Solon SFS

This project uses Solon SFS.

Before planning or editing, read:

- `SFS.md`
- `.sfs-local/VERSION`
- `.sfs-local/divisions.yaml`
- recent files under `.sfs-local/sprints/`
- recent files under `.sfs-local/decisions/`

Claude Code can use the project slash command:

- `/sfs`
- `/sfs help`
- `/sfs status`
- `/sfs start <goal>`
- `/sfs plan`
- `/sfs review`
- `/sfs decision <decision>`
- `/sfs retro`

Preserve user work. Ask only when a decision changes behavior or could discard work.
